---
title: Cheesy Bacon & Veggie Grilled Gnocchi with Sugo Sauce & Rocket-Pear Salad
description: Soft pillowy bundles of potato gnocchi, smothered in cheese and bacon and baked until deliciously golden and oozy. Now, if that hasn’t got your mouth watering, wait until you pull this dish of bubbling goodness from your oven.

*Keep an eye out... Due to recent sourcing challenges, we’ve replaced radish with tomato, which may be a little different to what’s pictured. Don’t worry, your recipe will be just as delicious!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cheesy-veggie-loaded-baked-gnocchi-87194ecc.jpg
